VERBATIM {
M4_17 {
@ Space between Mn and neighboring (Vn or Vn-1) when either Mn or (Vn or Vn-1) connects to >2.5v and ≤3.3v net.
@ DRC doesn't check Mn which the neighboring (Vn or Vn-1) is landed.	≥	0.11
 ((EXT M4i_voltage_33 V3i < 0.11 ABUT < 90 SINGULAR REGION EXTENTS MEASURE ALL) INTERACT M4i>1 ) NOT INSIDE MARKS
