SETLAYER  Z78 = ((MOMDMY INTERACT MOMMK7) INTERACT MOMMK8) NOT INTERACT (OR MOMMK1 MOMMK2 MOMMK3 MOMMK4 MOMMK5 MOMMK6)
OUTLAYER  (Z78 NOT WITH TEXT \"momcap78\" MOMDMY) NOT MARKS
}

