@ 1)V1 in MOMMK1 
@ 2)Vn/Vn-1 in MOMMKn (n=2~8), whereVn-1 is the via underneath Mn, and Vn is the via above Mn. Vn can be inter-via or TV1 or TV2.

for { set j 1 } { $j <= 7 } { incr j } {
OUTLAYER (V${j}i AND MOMMK${j}) NOT MARKS
