@ The space between (Mn AND MOMMKn AND MOMDMY) and Vn /Vn-1 (n=1~8) outside of MOMDMY, 
@ whereVn-1 is the via underneath Mn, and Vn is the via above Mn. Vn can be inter-via or TV1 or TV2.	≥	0.08	um

set j 1
